    "source_file": "RIS_Template.xlsx",
    "sheets": {
      "RIS": "Blank print-ready template (no placeholders)",
      "RIS with Mapping": "Same layout with placeholder tokens injected into data-entry cells"
    },
    "effective_data_range": "A1:I61",
    "item_table_range": "A12:I54",
    "item_table_repeatable": true,
    "item_table_max_rows_per_page": 43,
    "notes": [
      "Columns D and J–O are either structurally empty or used solely for merged-cell span; they carry no standalone data.",
      "The mapping sheet uses row 12 as a single representative row showing all item-table placeholders. In production, rows 12–54 are the repeatable data rows.",
      "Column D is spanned by C:D merges throughout the item table (Description field). No separate D column data exists.",
      "Rows beyond 65 in the sheet contain residual row-height metadata artifacts from the source file; they are not part of the form layout."
    ]
  },

